{
  "stem": "1753.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Zbaszyn on the border where, still, many of the refugees already had left and were able to get resettled, either in Poland, or outside Poland, or whatever-- the cities.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some, in fact, even had permission to go back to Germany, collect their property, and then migrated to some other parts of the world.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because of our limited means, our family couldn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But finally-- I would say, it must have been about one or two months later, it must-- no, it must have been in July of that year, my brother and I, we were able to enter an Ord school, that famous Ord school, even way back then.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were able to-- they took us to Poznan, a city in Pomerania, which, at one time, even in fact, before World War I, belonged to Germany.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then, it was-- became part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we were then in Poznan.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we learned the metal trade by-- in-- in a-- in a-- in a factory, Jewish-owned tool factory, and with, perhaps, 25 or 30 other young Jewish men.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they put us up in some-- in-- in-- in-- in a home where we lived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they fed us and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was funded by the American Ord.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, right now, because of-- I remember then, I'm very much involved in the Ord organization and support them, the best I can.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so that was in-- in July.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So it was July, August.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One day, it was September 1, 1939, the boss from the factory, a Jewish man by the name of Ignac Tuch, he came and talked to us and said, a war has started, and the Germans attacked Poland.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He asked us to go home.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
